HARD SKILLS:
GDPR Compliance • TCF 2.0 Implementation • Consent Management • Privacy Engineering • HbbTV • JavaScript • TypeScript • Node.js • Compliance Architecture • Testing Strategies • Monitoring • API Design • Requirements Analysis

SOFT SKILLS:
Technical Leadership • Risk Management • Stakeholder Communication • Cross-Functional Collaboration • Legal/Technical Translation • Problem Solving • Attention to Detail • Accountability • Decision-Making Under Pressure • Strategic Thinking

METRICS:
• Revenue Protected: 30M euros annually

